To automate the server configuration we shall use Bash Script, However there will be delay in configuring each and every server.

To automate the server configuration we will make use of tools to reduce the configuring time.
------------------------------------------------------------
Server Configuring Tools: CHEF, PUPPET, SALTSTACK, ANSIBLE
------------------------------------------------------------

ANSIBLE: Ansible is open source server configuring tool owned by redhat. With ansible you can configure Server, Tools, Network. Ansible perform tasks on server simultaneously thereby reducing the configuration time.

Ansible Has following things:
    Host
    Inventory
    Playbooks
    Core Modules
    Custom Modules
    Plugins


